The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v. Irving Leibowitz, Appellant.

(Republished)

Order, entered August 4, 1960, denying defendant’s application for a writ of error coram nobis, unanimously affirmed. No opinion, Concur — Breitel, J. P., Rabin, Valente, Stevens and Eager, JJ.
